Metode Agglomerative

m <- c("single","complete","ward", "average")
names(m) <- c("single","complete","ward", "average") 
ac <- function(x){
     agnes(PCA_scale_scores,method=x)$ac
   }
map_dbl(m,ac)

Metode Ward
